CSTutor.Model.Manager

Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • CSTutor.Model.Manager.Manager

  • public class Manager
extends java.lang.Object
    The Manager object is based on section 2.2 of the requirements. The manager contains a collection of classes. The selectedClass is the currently selected class, and the selectedSection is the currently selected section within that class.
